      "content": "It is very important that you do not mix diazepam with alcohol, including wine. Combining them can dangerously increase the sedative effects, leading to excessive drowsiness, impaired coordination, and in severe cases, respiratory depression. Please stick strictly to your prescribed dosage of diazepam and do not add any alcohol to your system. If you are having trouble sleeping, please discuss alternative, safe options with your prescribing doctor.",
