      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about drinking a whole bottle lol. just like a single glass of wine with my evening meal? it doesn't seem like that much to cause a big problem. i just really need to sleep tonight and i'm worried the diazepam won't be enough on its own if i'm this stressed.",
